results.cleanName: Duel Decks Elves vs Inventors Box Set

extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value: Elves vs. Inventors is the final release in the Duel Decks line.  The product includes two read-to-play 60-card decks that each carry a specific theme, and include a foil mythic rare card in each deck.  The package also contains 10 token cards, 2 spindown life counters, 2 deck boxes, a strategy insert, and a quick reference guide.
